267
00:16:43,030 --> 00:16:44,910
magiging isang kamangha-manghang karanasan.

268
00:16:47,200 --> 00:16:49,240
Hindi ko kailanman inisip na ang isang makamundong tao ay katulad mo

269
00:16:49,240 --> 00:16:52,640
