itong bolang gawa sa dagta ng pino bilang saksi.

308
00:18:30,920 --> 00:18:31,590
Kasunduan 'yan.

309
00:18:32,200 --> 00:18:32,720
Oo,

310
00:18:33,160 --> 00:18:33,960
