312
00:18:36,880 --> 00:18:38,810
Pigain mo lang, at magiging maayos din ito.

313
00:18:43,200 --> 00:18:43,830
Zhen.

314
00:18:46,640 --> 00:18:47,310
Salamat.

315
00:18:54,750 --> 00:18:55,550
