Isa itong pangako.

319
00:19:09,030 --> 00:19:10,680
Deal. Deal 'yan.

320
00:19:17,350 --> 00:19:18,960
-Binabati kita.
-Binabati kita.

321
00:19:18,960 --> 00:19:19,720
Salamat.

322
00:19:20,550 --> 00:19:21,310
Salamat.

