Oo, oo.

337
00:19:55,640 --> 00:19:57,570
Salamat sa pagsama sa biyahe, Jin.

338
00:19:58,030 --> 00:19:58,790
Jingdong

339
00:19:59,160 --> 00:20:01,440
Pinatahimik ko ang sarili ko at kinaladkad

340
